				<main id="main" class=""><article class="main-content"><h1 class="">Loving Municipal School District</h1>

				<p class="">Loving Municipal Schools is the source of great pride and the hub of activity in the village of Loving, New Mexico. It’s a great time to be a Loving Falcon. We are a community—a team of educators, learners, and families vested in educating the future leaders, thinkers, and innovators of not only our own community but of our state, nation, and our world.</p>
<p class="">We invite you to see what Loving Municipal Schools has to offer you and your family. From 1:1 technology to a strong athletics program to college prep, we have the tools and know-how to prepare students to pursue their dreams.</p>

<h2 class="">A Message from Our Superintendent </h2>
<p class="">We are all facing an unprecedented health emergency throughout our country. Collectively, we must remain calm and continue to support one another. Our focal point should remain with the students, because their success depends on it. Parents, please support us by having your child continue to read. Staff, please continue providing valuable resources for parents and students to use at home. We will continue to provide updates through our social media as they become available to us. Thank you.</p>
<div class="signature">Lee White</div>
<p class=""><a href="mailto:lwhite@lovingschools.org" title="" alt="" target="_top" class="">Lee White</a></p>
